1510
01:20:53,950 --> 01:20:57,718
<i>We saw truth not through
telling you what we thought,</i>

1511
01:20:57,720 --> 01:21:01,455
<i>but through a different
ethical approach to filmmaking</i>

1512
01:21:02,724 --> 01:21:06,060
<i>that allowed the world
to reveal itself to us.</i>

1513
01:21:06,062 --> 01:21:08,362
I do know that
documentaries are over.

1514
01:21:08,364 --> 01:21:10,431
Are you kidding?
It's what everyone is doing.

1515
01:21:10,433 --> 01:21:13,167
His documentaries are over.
What you're doing
is something else.

1516
01:21:13,169 --> 01:21:16,570
