1529
01:22:03,652 --> 01:22:05,986
<i>What else can I tell you?</i>

1530
01:22:05,988 --> 01:22:09,723
<i>After all these years,</i>
<i>I still don't have</i>
<i>all the answers.</i>

1531
01:22:09,725 --> 01:22:13,193
<i>And for the sake
of documentary cinema,</i>

1532
01:22:13,195 --> 01:22:16,964
<i>I intend to leave it that way.</i>
