1555
01:23:13,688 --> 01:23:16,256
I mean,
I'm not that good a writer.

1556
01:23:16,258 --> 01:23:18,425
If I made it all up, I'd be
the best writer in Hollywood

1557
01:23:18,427 --> 01:23:20,961
and, and Kent would be
Marlon Brando.

1558
01:23:20,963 --> 01:23:22,997
I never said it was amazing.
I just said it was faked.

1559
01:23:22,999 --> 01:23:24,365
And some of the timeline
was adjusted...

1560
01:23:24,367 --> 01:23:25,866
Would you stop
with the timeline crap?

1561
01:23:25,868 --> 01:23:27,968
Jamie knew that Kent
had tried to kill himself.

1562
01:23:27,970 --> 01:23:31,739
That he'd been in Afghanistan.
We didn't just stumble
upon it. It was rigged.

1563
01:23:31,741 --> 01:23:34,942
